<NEW>

"Because we have such a new and powerful leader." HELLSCREAM said. It
was obviously a lie, but he took off to help put the fires out, along
with DIRGEGUN, THRUSTOR and MAX-B.

It took only a few minutes to realize that these soldiers were made
for war, not for the putting out of the fires they made. However try
they did.

The fire was beginning to burn itself out, leaving most of the based
ruined. The jets were still flying around it trying to save what they
could. However the whole base seemed to be slowly sinking.

(TAG)

- Preston
